===Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-other-e|tabl|e|}}

#To put on a table.
#(''mostly British'') To propose for [[discussion]] (from ''to put on the table'')
#(''mostly US'') To hold back to a later time; to [[postpone]].
#:"The legislature '''tabled''' the amendment."
#To [[tabulate]]; to put into a table.

